      <title>最高法院裁定特朗普可以出现在总统选举中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-rules-trump-can-appear-on-presidential-ballots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，唐纳德·特朗普今年可以参加总统选举，从而结束了根据一项很少使用的禁止叛乱分子担任总统的宪法条款来禁止他的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-rules-trump-can-appear-on-presidential-ballots</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普首席财务官韦塞尔伯格将在纽约案件中承认伪证罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-to-plead-guilty-to-perjury-in-ny-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普房地产公司前首席财务官艾伦·韦塞尔伯格已被拘留，他准备承认在纽约州针对前总统的民事欺诈案中提供的证词中的伪证罪。此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-to-plead-guilty-to-perjury-in-ny-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核电站被扣押两年后，俄罗斯将接待联合国核监督机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/russia-to-host-un-nuclear-watchdog-two-years-after-plant-seizure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫从乌克兰夺取欧洲最大核电站两年后，联合国最高核官员计划在莫斯科会见俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京，作为敏感外交任务的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/russia-to-host-un-nuclear-watchdog-two-years-after-plant-seizure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国带头呼吁为欧盟国防计划提供可靠的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/france-leads-call-for-solid-options-to-fund-eu-defense-programs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国与波兰和爱沙尼亚一起呼吁欧盟为国防计划动员“充足”和“具体”的资金，并建议采用类似于大流行期间部署联合债券的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/france-leads-call-for-solid-options-to-fund-eu-defense-programs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
