    <item>
      <title>拜登预计特朗普将挑战 2024 年大选失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/biden-foresees-trump-challenging-2024-election-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登预测，如果他在 2024 年总统选举中失利，他可能的共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普将寻求推翻选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/biden-foresees-trump-challenging-2024-election-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:21:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰敦促欧盟禁止从俄罗斯和白俄罗斯进口食品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/poland-pushes-eu-to-ban-food-imports-from-russia-and-belarus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克表示，波兰将呼吁欧盟委员会全面禁止从俄罗斯和白俄罗斯进口食品，以加强该地区的安全并保护农民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/poland-pushes-eu-to-ban-food-imports-from-russia-and-belarus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理助手再次呼吁降息以援助经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/thai-pm-aide-renews-call-for-interest-rate-cuts-to-aid-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行面临政府阵营重新开始放松货币政策的呼吁，总理斯雷塔·塔维辛的高级助手认为，东南亚第二大经济体需要更便宜的借贷成本来刺激增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/thai-pm-aide-renews-call-for-interest-rate-cuts-to-aid-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融资法案禁止中国购买美国石油储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/china-barred-from-buying-from-oil-reserve-in-us-funding-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周日公布的必须通过的政府融资法案中的一项规定，中国将被禁止从美国紧急库存中购买石油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/china-barred-from-buying-from-oil-reserve-in-us-funding-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 21:08:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院可能周一对特朗普的投票资格做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/supreme-court-to-issue-opinion-monday-with-ballot-case-pending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院暗示，它可能会在周一就禁止唐纳德·特朗普参加科罗拉多州总统选举投票的努力做出裁决，并在选民准备前往科罗拉多州投票之际，在其日历中增加一个新的意见日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/supreme-court-to-issue-opinion-monday-with-ballot-case-pending</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
